# integration-workflows

The integration patterns with Total Expert CRM implement several specialized workflows:

## Bi-directional Sync
- Real-time synchronization of lead data and contact information between the Voice AI system and Total Expert
- Automatic propagation of lead status changes and disposition codes
- Custom field mapping for mortgage-specific data points

## Disposition Logging
Implemented in pages/Product.tsx:
- Automated logging of all contact attempts and outcomes
- Structured disposition codes aligned with mortgage industry standards
- Integration of compliance status into disposition records

## Appointment Setting
- Direct calendar sync with Total Expert for loan officer availability
- Automated appointment creation with contact details
- Real-time conflict detection and rescheduling logic

## CRM Integration Points
Key workflows include:
- Lead score calculation and synchronization
- Automated handoff to loan officers based on qualification criteria
- Compliance status verification before CRM updates

